commit.message:
Make it possible to set timeout explicitly

The timeout for authenticate() and acct_mgmt() functions
can be set by providing an additional argument or via
an application enviroment variable `request_timeout`.

If unset, the default value is 5000 milliseconds to resemble
old behaviour.
Install libpam headers when doing hex task
Don't fail build if configure was not run
Install pam library development files also when running Cover
Add support to send C coverage. Don't cache. Move hex plugin to Action
Use COVERALLS environment variable to detect when coveralls is required
Switch from Travis to Github Actions
Add Github Action to release to hex.pm when tagging

commit.message:
Update .travis.yml

Adding the below fix under before_install to make it run for Erlang23.0 on ppc64le with Ubuntu16.04
- if [ "$TRAVIS_ARCH" = "ppc64le" ]; then sudo apt-get update; sudo apt-get install rebar; fi
